rows.label: tlk43200141_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I love Bajena Playhouse, me. It's my
favorite theater.

rows.label: tlk43200141_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I go every single day! Until my money
runs out, I mean.

rows.label: tlk43200141_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I hope I'll get to walk out on that
stage someday as a leading lady!

rows.label: tlk43200141_01_msg0004
rows.name:
I'd bring Cole-san's scripts to life! I'd make
them laugh! Make them cry!
